thread.title: Patriots vs. Eagles: 5 Things to Watch in the Super Bowl

author: Jared Diamond
title: Patriots vs. Eagles: 5 Things to Watch in the Super Bowl
text:
Super Bowl Sunday has arrived, with the New England Patriots and Philadelphia Eagles set to square off at 6:30 p.m. ET at U.S. Bank Stadium in Minneapolis. The Patriots will seek their sixth championship this century, while the Eagles could win the Super Bowl for the first time in franchise history.
Here are five keys that will likely determine which team goes home with the Lombardi Trophy:
